- All views should follow the MVC pattern strictly.
- Use `@login_required` or permission decorators where relevant.
- Render views using shared components: cards, tiles, or status bars via `base_dashboard.html`.
- Use Materialize CSS classes for layout (`container`, `row`, `col s12`, etc.) unless intentionally diverging.

- Each dashboard module must be testable and reloadable independently (e.g. via HTMX or JS modules).
